bioContent.line: Born and raised in the Pacific Northwest, I am now a freshman at Rice University studying Computer Science and Mathematics.

My passion for computer science stems from my interest in Math, the enjoyment I find in strategic and analytical problem solving, and my belief that computer science holds the keys to solving many of the hardest problems faced today.
For these reasons I am expecially interested in AI, as well as the applications of deep learning to complex data sets and problems.
I have experience in Python and C/C++ as well as JavaScript, HTML, CSS, and React.
